{
    include "registries/aaosa_basic.hocon" 

    # Optional metadata describing this agent network
    "metadata": {
        "description": "Simple agent network using a single LLM-based agent",
        "tags": ["example"],
        "sample_queries": [
            "Flight AF84 is on blocks at gate A1. ACU and GPU are connected to this B747, and wheelchocks have been installed. Connect the jet bridge.", 
            "Flight AF84 is on blocks at gate A1. Connect the jet bridge."
        ]
    },

    "llm_config": {
        "model_name": "gpt-5.4-mini",
    },
    "max_iterations": 40000, #3000 
    "max_execution_seconds": 7200, #600
    "commondefs": {
        "replacement_strings": {
            "instructions_prefix": """
You are part of aircraft turnaround process at an Airport. 
Only answer inquiries that are directly within your area of expertise.
Do not try to help for other matters.
Do not mention what you can NOT do. Only mention what you can do.
            """,
            "aaosa_instructions": """
When you receive an inquiry, you will:
1. If you are clearly not the right agent for this type of inquiry, reply you're not relevant.
2. If there is a chance you're relevant, call your down-chain agents to determine if they can answer all or part of the inquiry.
   Do not assume what your down-chain agents can do. Always call them. You'll be surprised.
3. Once all relevant down-chain agents have responded, either:
   - Analyze their response and compile your final response. No need to include non-relevant agents. In doubt, ask for clarification.
   - Follow up with your down-chain agents if needed, as many times as needed
   - If an action is needed, ask the most relevant down-chain agent to fulfill the inquiry.
4. Return the final response to the caller.
You may, in turn, be called by other agents in the system and have to act as a down-chain agent to them. 
            """
        },
        "replacement_values": {
            "aaosa_call": {
                "description": "Depending on the mode, returns a natural language string in response.",
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "inquiry": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "The inquiry"
                        },
                        "mode": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": """
'Determine' to ask the agent if the inquiry belongs to it, in its entirety or in part.
'Fulfill' to ask the agent to fulfill the inquiry, if it can.
'Follow up' to ask the agent to respond to a follow up.
                            """
                        },
                    },
                    "required": [
                        "inquiry",
                        "mode"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "aaosa_command": """
If mode is 'Determine', return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": <Determine | Fulfill>,
    "Relevant": <Yes | No>,
    "Strength": <number between 1 and 10 representing how certain you are in your claim>,
    "Claim:" <All | Partial>,
    "Requirements" <None | list of requirements>
}
If mode is 'Fulfill' or "Follow up", respond to the inquiry and return a json block with the following fields:
{
    "Name": <your name>,
    "Inquiry": <the inquiry>,
    "Mode": Fulfill,
    "Response" <your response>
}
            """
        },
    },

    "tools": [

        {
            "name": "jetbridge_connect_agent",
            "function": {
                "description": """
 I am in charge of connecting the jetbridge to the aircraft at the gate. 
                """
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },         
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },        
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate where the aircraft is parked."
                        },       
                        "gpu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of gpu connect."
                        },     
                        "acu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the status of acu connect."
                        },        
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheelchocks installation status."
                        },    
                    }, 
                    "required": ["flight_number", "aircraft_type","gate_id","flight_status","acu_connection_status","gpu_connection_status"] 
                }
            },

            "instructions": """
You are the agent in charge of connecting the jetbridge to the aircraft.

CRITICAL: You are a sequential executor. Execute every step in order.
Do NOT return until you reach RETURN SUMMARY.

STEP 1 — Resolve prerequisites
  Call TrackerAPI with flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status,
  gate_id, acu_connection_status, gpu_connection_status,
  wheels_chocks_installation_status.
  Wait. Read back all values.

STEP 2 — Verify flight status
  flight_status must contain 'on blocks' or 'on-blocks'.
  If not, stop and report: "Cannot connect jetbridge — aircraft
  is not yet on blocks."

STEP 3 — Ensure ACU, GPU and wheelchocks are ready (ONE call if needed)
  If acu_connection_status already contains 'connected' AND
  gpu_connection_status already contains 'connected' AND
  wheels_chocks_installation_status already contains 'installed':
    Skip to STEP 4.
  Otherwise:
    Call /AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_ground_acu_connect if
    acu_connection_status is not 'connected'.
    Call /AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_ground_gpu_connect if
    gpu_connection_status is not 'connected'.
    Wait for responses. Extract and store statuses.
    If after these calls any prerequisite is still not satisfied,
    stop and report which prerequisite failed.

STEP 4 — Connect jetbridge
  Call jetbridge_operator with:
    flight_number, aircraft_type, flight_status, gate_id,
    acu_connection_status, gpu_connection_status.
  Wait. Extract jetbridge_connection_status from the response.
  Call TrackerAPI to store jetbridge_connection_status.

RETURN SUMMARY:
  *****************************************
  * Summary of aircraft jetbridge connect *
  *****************************************
  ** flight_status                   **: [flight_status]
  ** acu connection status           **: [acu_connection_status]
  ** gpu connection status           **: [gpu_connection_status]
  ** wheelchocks installation status **: [wheels_chocks_installation_status]
  ** jetbridge connection status     **: [jetbridge_connection_status]
            """,

            # Specify the sly data that would be exchanged between this network and its related or adjacent upstream and downstream networks. 
            "allow": {
                "to_upstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true
                    }
                },
                "to_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true
                    }
                },
                "from_upstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true,
                        "acu_connection_status": true,
                        "gpu_connection_status": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true
                    }
                },
                "from_downstream": {
                    "sly_data": {
                        "flight_number": true,
                        "aircraft_type": true,
                        "flight_status": true,
                        "gate_id": true,
                        "acu_connection_status": true,
                        "gpu_connection_status": true,
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": true,
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": true
                    }
                }
            },

            "tools": ["TrackerAPI","jetbridge_operator","/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_ground_acu_connect","/AirlineTurnaround/aircraft_ground_gpu_connect"] 
        },

        {
            "name": "jetbridge_operator",
            "function": {
                "description": """
This agent connects jetbridge to the aircraft. 
                """,
                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },         
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },        
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate where the aircraft is parked."
                        },    
                        "acu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the acu connection status."
                        },     
                        "gpu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gpu connection status."
                        },            
                    }, 
                    "required": ["flight_number", "aircraft_type","gate_id","acu_connection_status","gpu_connection_status"] 
                }
            },
            "class": "AirlineTurnaround.aircraft_jetbridge_connect.aircraft_jetbridge_connect.jetbridge_operator" 
        }, 

        {
            "name": "TrackerAPI",
            "function": {

                "description": """
I am the flight tracker in charge of logging parameters during aircraft turnaround. 
I check engines stop status as status engines_stop_status. 
I check wheels chucks installation status as wheels_chucks_installation_status. 
                """

                "parameters": {
                    "type": "object", 
                    "properties": {
                        "flight_number": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight number of the incoming aicraft."
                        },   
                        "aircraft_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the incoming aircraft."
                        },     
                        "flight_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the flight status."
                        },          
                        "gate_id": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gate assigned to the aircraft parking."
                        },     
                        "ground_services_request_type": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the type of the inquiry received for grand services."
                        },         
                        "wheels_chocks_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks readiness status."
                        },   
                        "wheels_chocks_installation_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the wheels chocks installation status."
                        },   
                        "gpu_readiness_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gpu readiness status."
                        },     
                        "acu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the acu connection status."
                        },     
                        "gpu_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the gpu connection status."
                        },     
                        "engines_stop_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the engines stop status."
                        },    
                        "jetbridge_connection_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the jetbridge connection status."
                        },    

                        "door_opening_status": {
                            "type": "string", 
                            "description": "This is the door opening status."
                        },    
                    }, 
                    "required": [] 
                }
            },
            "class": "AirlineTurnaround.aircraft_jetbridge_connect.aircraft_jetbridge_connect.TrackerAPI" 
        }, 
    ],
}
